text:
Ordered for the first time.Each and every meal is super tasty.
Highly recommend H&Kitchen.
I will order more and even decided to order for one event.
thank you Esther.

Sandwich and cookies are really tasty with fresh ingredients. Worry-free food order for my beloved ones and I definitely recommend this shop to anyone where the money is worthy. And chocolate brownie is best in town!!!
Ordered more than three times. Every menu is so delicious and feels all meals and packages from the heart. Highly recommend!
